{"tid":1897046,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"印度新德里爆示威 一警員被磚頭撃中死亡","createTime":"2020-02-25T13:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T13:53:44.000Z","uid":158504,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11aff188d62d12944183991b749903461ce57e1f","tid":1897046,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:19:21.000Z","msg":"印度修訂《公民身份法》再起衝突 新德里7人死<br />\n2020-02-25 HKT 16:15<br />\n<br />\n印度持續有民眾就修訂《公民身份法》引發的爭議，上街示威。新德里東北部多地發生衝突並引發騷亂，至少7人死亡，其中一名警員在衝突中殉職，另有150多人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，衝突在周一下午發生，支持與反對《公民身份法》修正案的民眾互扔磚頭，期間有人開槍。一名警員頭部被磚頭撃中死亡，另有多人中槍身亡。<br />\n<br />\n報道指警方向衝突雙方發射催淚彈，並禁止4人以上聚集。為防暴力升級，新德里地區多個地鐵站關閉，部分學校宣布停課。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510674-20200225.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510674-20200225.htm&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWD1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=c94bbf30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510674-20200225.htm&h=ee0ef548\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510674-20200225.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e505b76e0c3b07497a0c56fe46491f38c00e61a8","tid":1897046,"uid":281388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"3 萬 thanks"},{"pid":"58ea4fbd79baff49a57854adf9b3db486f591c0b","tid":1897046,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:21:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cea657a6fd4a8193eec5973072e1094ae9748c8a","tid":1897046,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:28:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"567804960225cb57e8823b52d3343dd0940d0988","tid":1897046,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike